        <abstract> 
<p>Pleased to hear of Peter Henderson’s intended experiment [on <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>, see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">10588</hi>]. Asks that she tell Mr Henderson that he believes good derived from animal diet will be shown only by production of larger number of seeds and more luxuriant growth in the ensuing year. Wishes to hear the results.</p> 
